Q: Write a C++ program to compute the average of three numbers.
A: Here is a simple C++ program to compute the average of three numbers:

```cpp
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
  int num1, num2, num3;
  double average;

  cout << "Enter three numbers: ";
  cin >> num1 >> num2 >> num3;

  average = (num1 + num2 + num3) / 3.0;

  cout << "The average is: " << average << endl;

  return 0;
}
```
